sub_title: New Media and Digital Culture student at the UvA, open for opportunities in media production.
summary:
I have an interest in New Media and finding new ways to reach viewers/customers. I also graduated in Interactive Media Theory at Masaryk University in 2016.

I am a fast learner and always looking for new opportunities for personal and professional growth. Co-workers come to me with technical issues and time management problems.

My professional and free time go hand in hand. I like to make videos, photograph and paint with watercolours. 

Specialities: Production, Social Media, Time Management, Entertainment, TV technology, Photography, Video, Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat, Twitter, YouTube, Broadcasting.
